[09:52] <dalek> parrot:     + Added a Parrot_{un,}block_GC_move API for the 2 string compacting
[09:52] <dalek> parrot:       collectors ms and ms2
[09:52] <dalek> parrot:     + Deprecated ListChunk GC API and src/list.c GH #1179
[09:52] <dalek> parrot:     + Fixed a --gc=ms segv in Parrot_io_write_s GH #1196
[09:52] <dalek> parrot:     + const/ARGIN all read-only IO api arguments
[09:52] <dalek> parrot:     + Fixed --gc=inf string header allocation and failing tests
[09:52] <dalek> parrot: - Build
[09:52] <dalek> parrot:     + --optimize: Replace -O2 from perl5 with -O3 on clang or gcc. GH #1185
[09:52] <dalek> parrot:       5% faster
[09:52] <dalek> parrot:     + Fixed make clean realclean and install which sometimes forgot pmc_default.h
[09:52] <dalek> parrot:       GH #1194, GH #1206
[09:52] <dalek> parrot: - Tests
[09:52] <dalek> parrot:     + Use the faster travis docker infrastructure without sudo
